{"tid":1708352,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯要票既入黎","createTime":"2019-11-11T14:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:41:39.000Z","uid":127532,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf90ea01af2b0198e4552f0723bc2ac0b00a4cd","tid":1708352,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"我本身淺黃，屋企大部分親戚都係藍<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地好憎示威者，但佢地最想係社會回復正常</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好明顯，依家最大問題係警民衝突<br />\n班親戚開始明白，警察武力升級係唔會令示威罷休，反而會令問題加劇<br />\n雖然佢地唔鐘意示威者，但都認為成立獨立調查委員會係最有效平息風波既方法<br />\n咁多年無論區議會定立法會，佢地都投開建制派，但今次有好多話會投泛民<br />\n點解？因為佢地認為泛民會爭取獨立調查警暴<br />\n佢地認為一旦有獨立調查，大部份市民都會收貨，社會好快就會回復正常<br />\n<br />\n民建聯，你自己知自己事，今次選舉你輸硬<br />\n我依家同你講條件，你肯跟既，唔單只攞到我果票，我仲會說服親戚投俾你<br />\n條件就係︰公開向政府施壓，要求成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n有無人跟機？跟機既幫推 post，愈多人跟愈有可能成事"},{"pid":"83f344e5da2700aa18d800ae1f584e1ca5a5fa6a","tid":1708352,"uid":137080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"叫人投民賤聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負皮 上一頁"},{"pid":"291fbe5e141885a48d0cfc8baea5d36ec5841e6d","tid":1708352,"uid":127532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83f344e5da2700aa18d800ae1f584e1ca5a5fa6a","tid":1708352,"uid":137080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"叫人投民賤聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負皮 上一頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:30:29.000Z","msg":"連登仔既智商有無咁低"},{"pid":"dccf255c884c50a52b02dab3a8954fbac7ebf96c","tid":1708352,"uid":324877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf90ea01af2b0198e4552f0723bc2ac0b00a4cd","tid":1708352,"uid